{1 API reference}

wodoc is also an OCaml library: the same passes the [wodoc] command-line tool
chains are exposed as modules. See the {{!page-"api"}API overview}, or jump to
{!Wodoc.Preprocess}, {!Wodoc.Render}, {!Wodoc.Assemble} and {!Wodoc.Convert}.

{1 Status}

Early work in progress. wodoc is developed in the
{{:https://github.com/ocsigen/wodoc}ocsigen/wodoc} repository and distributed
under the MIT license.
